# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:12
translate chinese english3_8b8bb224:

    # "The school-day goes by normally until my English class."
    "学校的一天平平淡淡地过着，直到英语课。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:13
translate chinese english3_66510385:

    # "Mrs. McGee has us working on essays in class. Everyone is quiet, looking down at their papers."
    "麦基夫人让我们在课堂上写作文。大家都安静地低头看着自己的纸。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:14
translate chinese english3_3d0d4f25:

    # "But I feel like somebody is watching me."
    "但我感觉好像有人在盯着我。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:17
translate chinese english3_0ba62eb9:

    # "I look up at see Mrs. McGee gazing at me. Staring. A slight smile on her face."
    "我抬头一看，发现麦基夫人正注视着我。她凝视着我，脸上挂着一丝微笑。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:18
translate chinese english3_e3525f66:

    # "I wonder what she could be thinking about?"
    "她在想什么呢？"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:21
translate chinese english3_2d0786b4:

    # "She smiles, moving her hand close to her mouth."
    "她微笑着，把手移到嘴边。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:22
translate chinese english3_8c67e0d6:

    # "I look around at the other students surrounding me, but their eyes are all focused on the essays they are writing."
    "我环顾四周，周围的同学都埋头写着作文。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:23
translate chinese english3_342debb3:

    # "There is no doubt that Mrs. McGee's gaze is meant for me and me alone."
    "毫无疑问，麦基夫人的目光只锁定在我身上。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:26
translate chinese english3_48f33b68:

    # "While I am looking directly at her, she slips the tip of her index finger between her plump lips, sucking it sensually."
    "就在我直视她的瞬间，她将食指指尖滑入丰润的双唇之间，性感地吮吸着。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:27
translate chinese english3_3972cbcf:

    # "Her eyes never leave mine."
    "她的目光始终没有离开我。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:28
translate chinese english3_1596ea41:

    # "There is little doubt what she is thinking now. My cock twitches in my pants, thumping against the thin fabric."
    "她此刻在想什么，几乎毋庸置疑。我的鸡巴在裤子里抽动，重重地撞击着薄薄的布料。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:29
translate chinese english3_341dee20:

    # "Then Randy, the know-it-all asshole who always has something clever to say, speaks up and breaks our trance."
    "这时，那个自以为是、总爱耍嘴皮子的混蛋兰迪开口了，打破了我们的恍惚。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:32
translate chinese english3_52d7af01:

    # "Randy" "Mrs. McGee, my essay is done, can I leave?"
    "Randy" "“麦基老师，我的作文写完了，我可以走了吗？”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:33
translate chinese english3_937ce766:

    # "Mrs. McGee quickly looks up and straightens herself, as if she hasn't been thinking about dick for the last few minutes."
    "麦基老师迅速抬起头，挺直了身子，仿佛刚才那几分钟里她根本没在想鸡巴似的。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:34
translate chinese english3_82e82c18:

    # et "Yes Randy, you can leave."
    et "“可以，兰迪，你可以走了。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:35
translate chinese english3_90bacfb8:

    # et "In fact, any of you who are done with your essays, or would prefer to work on them at home, feel free to leave any time."
    et "“其实，你们当中谁写完了作文，或者想回家写，随时都可以离开。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:36
translate chinese english3_69be14c8:

    # "Most of the class stands up then and leaves, but I stay. So do Juliana and a few other people."
    "这时，班上大多数人都站起来离开了，但我留了下来。朱莉安娜和另外几个人也留了下来。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:37
translate chinese english3_dd5bdbb5:

    # "I don't really have anywhere to go before the next class anyways."
    "反正下一节课之前我也没什么地方可去。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:39
translate chinese english3_44bea0f3:

    # "So I focus on getting my essay done, occasionally looking up at Mrs. McGee."
    "于是我专心写完论文，偶尔抬头看看麦基夫人。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:40
translate chinese english3_9fb697a3:

    # "She is focused on her work now, her eyes down on the desk in front of her."
    "她此刻正全神贯注地工作，目光低垂在面前的课桌上。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:41
translate chinese english3_166c1158:

    # "At the end of class, I stand up and get ready to leave."
    "下课时，我站起身准备离开。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:44
translate chinese english3_6f3f8621:

    # et "I appreciate you staying until the end of class."
    et "“感谢你一直待到下课。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:45
translate chinese english3_314047f4:

    # et "I know it wasn't the most exciting class today, but it's good that you're committed to learning."
    et "我知道今天的课可能不太有趣，但你对学习的投入让我很欣慰。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:49
translate chinese english3_3c2d53ef:

    # et "I'm glad. I hope we can continue sometime."
    et "我很高兴。希望以后还能继续交流。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:52
translate chinese english3_b244bcae:

    # et "Don't get in too much of a hurry."
    et "别太着急。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:53
translate chinese english3_398957e6:

    # et "Besides, my next class is coming in right now."
    et "再说，下一节课的学生马上就要进来了。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:58
translate chinese english3_db48971e:

    # et "Well, okay then."
    et "“那好吧。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:59
translate chinese english3_c08bcb72:

    # et "I'll see you next time, [pcname]."
    et "“下次见，[pcname]。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:60
translate chinese english3_9259ab8b:

    # et "You have a good day."
    et "“祝你今天过得愉快。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:61
translate chinese english3_66796d27:

    # pc "You too, Mrs. McGee."
    pc "“你也是，麦基夫人。”"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:64
translate chinese english3_d25b195e:

    # "I leave her class and go on to my next."
    "我离开她的教室，前往下一节课。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:65
translate chinese english3_764b5703:

    # "I can't get her out of my head though. She had definitely been coming on to me."
    "但我脑海里始终挥之不去她的身影。她显然是在向我示好。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:66
translate chinese english3_40a773cc:

    # "Isn't she married? I guess that doesn't stop some people."
    "她不是已婚了吗？看来这并不能阻止某些人。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:67
translate chinese english3_2358e52d:

    # "Still though, she is a teacher. And older than me."
    "不过话说回来，她毕竟是老师。而且比我年长。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:68
translate chinese english3_48dff846:

    # "Am I really into that?"
    "我真的对这种事感兴趣吗？"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:71
translate chinese english3_c15f3a61:

    # "She is hot as fuck. I want to see what she has going on under those dresses that she always wears."
    "她性感得要命。真想看看她总穿的那些连衣裙底下藏着什么。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:75
translate chinese english3_e434795b:

    # "She doesn't really have anything that interested me."
    "其实她没什么特别吸引我的地方。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:76
translate chinese english3_0cd18054:

    # "I try to push her out of my mind and concentrate on my classes."
    "我努力把她从脑海中赶出去，专心听课。"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:77
translate chinese english3_cf1b04ad:

    # "The rest of the day passes by uneventfully. Then I leave and go to work."
    "剩下的时间平平淡淡地过去了。然后我离开学校去上班。"

